      %p The pejorative suffixes #{t "-охе/-оха", "-ohe/-oha"} and #{t "-ухце/-уха", "-uhece/-uha"} are frequently used instead on bases with a negative connotation.
      - words = [ [ { :cyr => "старе", :lat => "stáre" },
