      %p The endings #{t "-оке", "-oke"}, #{t "-гло", "-glo"}, and #{t "-ане", "-áne"} turn a verb into some sort of tool or instrument used to perform that action. #{t "-Ане", "-áne"} also frequently derives nouns from other nouns.
